ts.support

Class TSString

  • java.lang.Object
    • ts.support.TSValue
      • ts.support.TSPrimitive
        • ts.support.TSString

  • public final class TSString
extends TSPrimitive
    Represents (Tscript) String values (ELS 8.4).

    This class only currently allows String values to be created and does not yet support operations on them.
